						<p><hi rend="bold">Undated. 10th cent. A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>Gift of five <hi rend="italic">kaḻañcus</hi> of gold for maintaing 50 lamps to the temple of Mahākāḷattu Mahādēva at Ambar by Ūrañchēndaṉ of Aṉaṅgavallappāḍi. The gold was received by the local residents (?) of the village and they agreed to maintain lamps.</p>						

